  "content": "<h1 class='section api' data-uid='Alis.Core.Ecs.Kernel.AddComponent' data-commentId='T:Alis.Core.Ecs.Kernel.AddComponent' id='Alis_Core_Ecs_Kernel_AddComponent'>Struct AddComponent    <a class='header-action link-secondary' title='View source' href='https://github.com/pabllopf/Alis/blob/master/4_Operation/Ecs/src/Kernel/AddComponent.cs#L43'><i class='bi bi-code-slash'></i></a></h1>\r\n <div class=\"facts text-secondary\">\r\n<dl><dt>Namespace</dt><dd><a href='Alis.Core.Ecs.Kernel.html'>Alis.Core.Ecs.Kernel</a></dd></dl><dl><dt>Assembly</dt><dd>Alis.dll</dd></dl>\r\n</div><p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Ecs.Kernel.AddComponent.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">Add component command</p>\n<pre><code class='lang-csharp'>public record struct AddComponent : IEquatable&lt;AddComponent&gt;</code></pre><h4 class='section'>Implements</h4><dl class=\"typelist\"><dd>\r\n<div>\n<a href='https://learn.microsoft.com/dotnet/api/system.iequatable-1'>IEquatable&lt;AddComponent&gt;</a>\n</div>\n\r\n</dd></dl><h4 class='section'>Inherited Members</h4><dl class=\"typelist\"><dd>\r\n<div>\n<a href='https://learn.microsoft.com/dotnet/api/system.object.equals#system-object-equals(system-object)'>object.Equals(object?)</a>\n</div>\n<div>\n<a href='https://learn.microsoft.com/dotnet/api/system.object.equals#system-object-equals(system-object-system-object)'>object.Equals(object?, object?)</a>\n</div>\n<div>\n<a href='https://learn.microsoft.com/dotnet/api/system.object.gethashcode'>object.GetHashCode()</a>\n</div>\n<div>\n<a href='https://learn.microsoft.com/dotnet/api/system.object.gettype'>object.GetType()</a>\n</div>\n<div>\n<a href='https://learn.microsoft.com/dotnet/api/system.object.referenceequals'>object.ReferenceEquals(object?, object?)</a>\n</div>\n<div>\n<a href='https://learn.microsoft.com/dotnet/api/system.object.tostring'>object.ToString()</a>\n</div>\n\r\n</dd></dl><h2 class='section'>Remarks</h2><p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Ecs.Kernel.AddComponent.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">Memory layout optimized: 12 bytes total (GameObjectIdOnly 6 bytes + ComponentHandle 6 bytes)\nPack = 1 for minimal memory footprint</p>\n<h2 class='section'>Constructors</h2><h3 class='section api' data-uid='Alis.Core.Ecs.Kernel.AddComponent.#ctor(Alis.Core.Ecs.Kernel.GameObjectIdOnly,Alis.Core.Ecs.Kernel.ComponentHandle)' data-commentId='M:Alis.Core.Ecs.Kernel.AddComponent.#ctor(Alis.Core.Ecs.Kernel.GameObjectIdOnly,Alis.Core.Ecs.Kernel.ComponentHandle)' id='Alis_Core_Ecs_Kernel_AddComponent__ctor_Alis_Core_Ecs_Kernel_GameObjectIdOnly_Alis_Core_Ecs_Kernel_ComponentHandle_'>AddComponent(GameObjectIdOnly, ComponentHandle)    <a class='header-action link-secondary' title='View source' href='https://github.com/pabllopf/Alis/blob/master/4_Operation/Ecs/src/Kernel/AddComponent.cs#L43'><i class='bi bi-code-slash'></i></a></h3>\r\n <p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Ecs.Kernel.AddComponent.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">Add component command</p>\n<pre><code class='lang-csharp'>public AddComponent(GameObjectIdOnly Entity, ComponentHandle ComponentHandle)</code></pre><h4 class='section'>Parameters</h4><dl class='parameters'><dt><code>Entity</code> <a href='Alis.Core.Ecs.Kernel.GameObjectIdOnly.html'>GameObjectIdOnly</a>  </dt>\r\n<dd>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Ecs.Kernel.AddComponent.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">The entity to add component to</p>\n\r\n</dd><dt><code>ComponentHandle</code> <a href='Alis.Core.Ecs.Kernel.ComponentHandle.html'>ComponentHandle</a>  </dt>\r\n<dd>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Ecs.Kernel.AddComponent.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">The component handle to add</p>\n\r\n</dd></dl><h4 class='section'>Remarks</h4><p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Ecs.Kernel.AddComponent.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">Memory layout optimized: 12 bytes total (GameObjectIdOnly 6 bytes + ComponentHandle 6 bytes)\nPack = 1 for minimal memory footprint</p>\n<h2 class='section'>Properties</h2><h3 class='section api' data-uid='Alis.Core.Ecs.Kernel.AddComponent.ComponentHandle' data-commentId='P:Alis.Core.Ecs.Kernel.AddComponent.ComponentHandle' id='Alis_Core_Ecs_Kernel_AddComponent_ComponentHandle'>ComponentHandle    <a class='header-action link-secondary' title='View source' href='https://github.com/pabllopf/Alis/blob/master/4_Operation/Ecs/src/Kernel/AddComponent.cs#L44'><i class='bi bi-code-slash'></i></a></h3>\r\n <p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Ecs.Kernel.AddComponent.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">The component handle to add</p>\n<pre><code class='lang-csharp'>public ComponentHandle ComponentHandle { readonly get; set; }</code></pre><h4 class='section'>Property Value</h4><dl class='parameters'><dt> <a href='Alis.Core.Ecs.Kernel.ComponentHandle.html'>ComponentHandle</a>  </dt>\r\n<dd>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n</dd></dl><h3 class='section api' data-uid='Alis.Core.Ecs.Kernel.AddComponent.Entity' data-commentId='P:Alis.Core.Ecs.Kernel.AddComponent.Entity' id='Alis_Core_Ecs_Kernel_AddComponent_Entity'>Entity    <a class='header-action link-secondary' title='View source' href='https://github.com/pabllopf/Alis/blob/master/4_Operation/Ecs/src/Kernel/AddComponent.cs#L44'><i class='bi bi-code-slash'></i></a></h3>\r\n <p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Ecs.Kernel.AddComponent.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">The entity to add component to</p>\n<pre><code class='lang-csharp'>public GameObjectIdOnly Entity { readonly get; set; }</code></pre><h4 class='section'>Property Value</h4><dl class='parameters'><dt> <a href='Alis.Core.Ecs.Kernel.GameObjectIdOnly.html'>GameObjectIdOnly</a>  </dt>\r\n<dd>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n</dd></dl>",
